              "customNotes": "Name: Leavers by Job\n\n**Do not display Title, suggestions**\n**Do not render a message list**\n**Render a pie chart only**\n\n**IMP - Do not add Title, not include anything in the title it should be **empty\n\n## Pie Chart Rules\n\n* Title: Leavers by Job\n* Each slice label: $Job\n* Each slice value: $EmpCount\n* Higher the $EmpCount, larger the slice priority/visibility\n\n**If $Job == `Unknown`, null, or empty, place it at the end of the dataset**\n**Sort all jobs by $EmpCount in descending order**\n**Use only the top 5 jobs with the highest count for the chart**\n**Return only structured chart data**"
